# Cursor respects .gitignore/.git-exclude for indexing and search (Glob/Grep) by
# default. That's right for build output and vendored/reference trees in general,
# but these specific paths are still actively read/searched by agents working in
# this repo, so explicitly re-include them here (negation overrides gitignore).
#
# See docs/README.md (in the decoupled docs/ repo) and
# .cursor/rules/reference-trees-gitignored.mdc for background.

!/BfaCore-Reforged/
!/docs/